OL,3,C20,000 renters will be 'pulled into
OL,4,Cpoverty' over housing allowance freeze
OL,6,FAnalysis shown exclusively to ITV News
OL,7,Ffound 20,000 renters, including 10,000
OL,8,Fchildren, will be paying hundreds of
OL,9,Fpounds extra on their rent if the
OL,10,Fgovernment doesn't rethink.
OL,12,FWith the Budget just over two weeks
OL,13,Faway, they're urging the government to
OL,14,Funfreeze Local Housing Allowance and
OL,15,Finstead link it to local rents, to
OL,16,Fhelp private renters.
