OL,3,C20,000 renters will be 'pulled into
OL,4,Cpoverty' over housing allowance freeze
OL,6,FLocal Housing Allowance (LHA) is the
OL,7,Frate used to determine how much extra
OL,8,Ffinancial support private renters on
OL,9,FUniversal Credit or housing benefit
OL,10,Fcan receive.
OL,12,FIt's currently set at a level that
OL,13,Fallows people to afford the bottom 30%
OL,14,Fof rental properties in their area.
OL,16,FThe analysis by the Joseph Rowntree
OL,17,FFoundation shows that if the Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment doesn't unfreeze LHA in the
OL,19,FBudget, private renters will be on
OL,20,Faverage #243 worse off by 2025-2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
