OL,11,FThe increase is even more for a
OL,12,Fworking age couple with children, who
OL,13,Fwould be #340 worse off.
OL,15,FIf the freeze continues until the end
OL,16,Fof this parliament in 2029, the
OL,17,Faverage private renter will be #703
OL,18,Fworse off, compared to #882 for a
OL,19,Fcouple with children.
