OL,6,FThe Joseph Rowntree Foundation thinks
OL,7,Fthis could drive 50,000 vulnerable
OL,8,Fprivate renters into poverty by the
OL,9,Fend of the parliament, including
OL,10,F30,000 children.
OL,12,FHousing and poverty campaigners say
OL,13,Fthe rising cost of rent means housing
OL,14,Fallowance doesn't go far enough.
OL,16,FOffice for National Statistics (ONS)
OL,17,Fprivate rent inflation figures out
OL,18,Ftoday also show rents in Great Britain
OL,19,Fincreased by 8.4%, an average of #93 a
OL,20,Fmonth, in the year to September 2024.
