OL,3,C20,000 renters will be 'pulled into
OL,4,Cpoverty' over housing allowance freeze
OL,6,FThe previous government temporarily
OL,7,Funfroze the allowance, but planned to
OL,8,Ffreeze it again from 2025 - charities
OL,9,Fwill be watching the Budget closely to
OL,10,Fsee if Rachel Reeves sticks with the
OL,11,Fprevious government's plan or responds
OL,12,Fto their calls.
OL,14,FBut Reeves has warned of "tough
OL,15,Fdecisions" in the Budget, as she tries
OL,16,Fto fill the #22 billion "black hole"
OL,17,Fin the public finances left by the
OL,18,Fprevious government and avoid a return
OL,19,Fto austerity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
